<script type="x-jquery-tmpl" id="tournamentBroadcastTmpl">

<script type="text/javascript">
    pgatour.Ad.addCreationCallback(function (config) {
        var pos = config.options.pos;
        if (pos.indexOf('row') === 0 || pos === 'my_lb_drawer' || pos === 'cutline') {
            config.suspendInitialization = true;
        }
    });
</script>
